exp = get_experiment_with_repeated_arms(2)
trial_index = 1
status_quo_features = ObservationFeatures(parameters=exp.trials[trial_index
    ].status_quo.parameters, trial_index=trial_index)
modelbridge = ModelBridge(get_search_space_for_value(), 0, [], exp, 0,
    status_quo_features=status_quo_features)
if len(exp.trials) >= 1:
    self.assertEqual(modelbridge.status_quo, get_observation_status_quo1())
mock.patch('ax.modelbridge.base.observations_from_data', autospec=True,
    return_value=[get_observation_status_quo0(),
